'''西西里披薩'''（{{lang-it|sfincione}}; [[西西里语|西西里语]]：sfinciuni）是[[義大利|義大利]][[西西里|西西里]]地區的披薩餅。西西里披薩起源於1890年代，最早流行於[[西西里島|西西里島]]的西部地區。之後西西里披薩傳到美國，並且外觀也發生了一些變化<ref name="Pantheon">{{cite journal|last=Powell|first=Welliam|title=Pantheon of Pies|journal=Cincinnati|date=November 2011|volume=45|issue=2|pages=63|url=http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/articles/67268938/pantheon-pies|accessdate=14 April 2013|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111044104/http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/articles/67268938/pantheon-pies|dead-url=no}}</ref>。傳統的西西里披薩的原料包括洋蔥、鳳尾魚、番茄、香料和奶酪<ref name="Classic">{{cite web|last=Hulin|first=Brenda|title=Classic Pizza Types|url=http://www.netplaces.com/pizza/pizza-basics/classic-pizza-styles.htm|work=Netplaces|accessdate=14 April 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515060807/http://www.netplaces.com/pizza/pizza-basics/classic-pizza-styles.htm|archivedate=2013年5月15日}}</ref>。在美國，西西里披薩則多為方形<ref>{{cite book |title=The Everything Travel Guide to Italy: A complete guide to Venice, Florence, Rome, and Capri |last=Kavin |first=Kim |authorlink= |coauthors= |year=2010 |publisher=Everything Books |location= |isbn=1605501662 |page=262 |pages= |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jFKot04PLSkC&pg=PA262&dq=sicilian+pizza&hl=en&sa=X&ei=mTSvUJbAFYrNiwLRk4H4CQ&ved=0CDoQ6AEwATgK#v=onepage&q=sicilian%20pizza&f=false |accessdate=November 2012 |archive-date=2016-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516021156/https://books.google.com/books?id=jFKot04PLSkC&pg=PA262&dq=sicilian+pizza&hl=en&sa=X&ei=mTSvUJbAFYrNiwLRk4H4CQ&ved=0CDoQ6AEwATgK#v=onepage&q=sicilian%20pizza&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
